            I concur with the hon. Gentleman's judgment about his constituency. I understand the particular problems that arise in rural areas. Would he not agree that the problem of accessibility is equally great in some inner-city constituencies with a disproportionate number of elderly people on low incomes and low car ownership?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0401P0-04373'>
        <a name='S6CV0401P0_20030312_WH_21'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-anthony-steen' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
