          <p class='first-para'>
            I am glad that I gave way. As the hon. Gentleman may know, I represented an inner-city seat in Liverpool for nine years. I am familiar with the points that he makes. The major supermarkets are on the outskirts of Liverpool, and to get there from the inner city is a day's job. The hon. Gentleman's point is extremely valid.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0401P0-04374'>
        <a name='S6CV0401P0_20030312_WH_22'>  </a>
