          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0401P0-04425'>
        <a name='S6CV0401P0_20030312_WH_73'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/dr-evan-harris' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0401P0_20030312_WH_73' title='Link to this speech by Dr Evan Harris' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-evan-harris" title="Dr Evan Harris">Dr. Harris</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
